{"title":"「一本通 6.1 练习 3」越狱","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/6028#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=6028","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/6028/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/6028/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/6028"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"\r\n\n监狱有连续编号为 $1$ 到 $n$ 的 $n$ 个房间，每个房间关押一个犯人。有 $m$ 种宗教，每个犯人可能信仰其中一种。如果相邻房间的犯人信仰的宗教相同，就可能发生越狱。求有多少种状态可能发生越狱。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入两个整数 $m$ 和 $n$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"可能越狱的状态数，对 $100003$ 取余。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n2 3\r\n```\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n6\r\n```\r\n#### 样例说明\r\n所有可能的 $6$ 种状态为：$\\{0,0,0\\},\\{0,0,1\\},\\{0,1,1\\},\\{1,0,0\\},\\{1,1,0\\},\\{1,1,1\\}$。"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于全部数据，$1\\le m\\le 10^8,1\\le n\\le 10^{12}$。"}]}